Description:
============
    Stubs out a new component with its respective template and test.
    Pass the component name, either CamelCased or under_scored, and an optional list of attributes as arguments.

Example:
========
    bin/rails generate action_view:component Profile name age

    creates a Profile action_view:component class, test and template:
        Component:    app/components/profile.rb
        Template:     app/components/profile.html.erb
        Test:         test/components/profile_test.rb
